Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.15,0:19:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,l can't sit idly by after seeing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The symbol of the evil Ternel, who was sealed away 300 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.39,0:19:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,l have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.87,0:20:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like l have nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.94,0:20:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,l was worried about that Flare girl too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.74,0:20:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,ls this the place, Lord Zeke?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's so bleak, not romantic in the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,lf we went to the hotel two towns back, it would be much nicer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,See, it's cramped back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Am l in for monsters? Snakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.81,0:21:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Lord Zeke!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to my mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.32,0:21:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm the mistress of this mansion, Ternel Pajan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.22,0:21:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What brings you to my estate?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,l apologize for the unannounced visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.53,0:21:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm a traveler named Zeke.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.13,0:21:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My car broke down. l was hoping to stay here until the repairs are finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.54,0:21:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that must be awful. l'll have a guest room prepared at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.27,0:21:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay for as long as you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.81,0:22:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you kindly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.02,0:22:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Zeke, wasn't that a little obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.89,0:22:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.76,0:22:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, Lord Zeke!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.79,0:22:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Am l gonna have to carry the luggage by myself again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow us to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.80,0:22:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We will carry your luggage to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.60,0:22:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.32,0:22:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,l can't leave these girls here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.32,0:22:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess l have to wait patiently for an opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.13,0:22:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This might be a bit too bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.23,0:22:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.00,0:22:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.04,0:22:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That mistress has her eyes on Lord Zeke!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.57,0:23:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,l can't let her win!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.68,0:23:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Zeke, would you like another cup of tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, l'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.58,0:23:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Zeke, could that box hold...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.22,0:23:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.42,0:23:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, maybe l'll hit the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.97,0:23:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Zeke...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.60,0:23:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be weary from your long journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.87,0:23:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,lf you'd like, l'll gladly wash your back for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.24,0:23:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,l'd like that a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.75,0:23:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,l hear lots of rumors out on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.58,0:23:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What sorts of rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.19,0:23:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, a giant devil appearing to protect a village from a fortress falling from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.66,0:23:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My, how interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.23,0:24:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's just a baseless rumor though.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.97,0:24:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any others? Please tell them to me, Master Zeke.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.14,0:24:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.11,0:24:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There is this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.38,0:24:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They say a beautiful mistress lived in a mansion somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.09,0:24:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They say word of her beauty has traveled all the way to distant lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.73,0:24:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She wed eventually, but her suitor turned out to be a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.94,0:24:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Word of her beauty had spread even into the monster realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.21,0:24:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, the man's true identity became known and the humans killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.00,0:25:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Then? What became of the woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.13,0:25:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, l cannot remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.50,0:25:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Zeke...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.84,0:25:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Zeke, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.41,0:25:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me, Lord Zeke!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.68,0:25:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This bath is way too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.08,0:25:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you shouldn't have wasted all that time bringing these items to the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.08,0:25:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,l need them! You never know what may happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.09,0:25:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You never know what may happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.59,0:25:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, never mind that, Lord Zeke.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.43,0:25:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,l smell another woman's scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.33,0:25:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're imagining things.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.26,0:25:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, guess l'm done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.66,0:25:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Oh, Lord Zeke!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.57,0:25:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What should l do with this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.80,0:25:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,lf you'd like...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.07,0:25:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd gladly wash your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.87,0:25:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Pl..Pl..Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.91,0:25:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,lt will be our pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.42,0:26:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do down there, Lony? You're sparkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.59,0:26:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They cleaned off about three years worth of grime.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.00,0:26:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How about someone else here cleans off three years worth of grime?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.90,0:26:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Though all that'll be left are wrinkles.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.77,0:26:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you referring to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.24,0:26:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,ls the food to your liking?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.31,0:26:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.94,0:26:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,ln fact, this entire mansion is gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.01,0:26:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But above all, l'd like to give a toast to your beauty, Lady Ternel.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.02,0:26:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You flatter me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.34,0:26:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, Lady Ternel.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.51,0:26:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,l remember the rest of that rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.18,0:26:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, do tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.85,0:27:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite the fact that he was a monster, the woman loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.22,0:27:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Day in and day out, for months, she sobbed before his ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.46,0:27:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And then one day, all of the villagers suddenly went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.23,0:27:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The person behind their disappearance was none other than the beautiful mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.54,0:27:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She sacrificed the villagers alive for killing the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.04,0:27:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She did this in order to become a monster, just like the man she loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.75,0:27:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,These events are said to have occurred 300 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.72,0:27:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fascinating story.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.19,0:27:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's all right, Mineru. lt's just thunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.50,0:27:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.00,0:27:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The day after a storm is always sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.44,0:28:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the legend, a hero sealed the monster-woman away.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.21,0:28:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,According to other versions, she's still alive someplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.61,0:28:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Zeke, what's that next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.25,0:28:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.19,0:28:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's like a charm of sorts, handed down within my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.76,0:28:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.36,0:28:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They say this blade can slay monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.90,0:28:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,l carry it with me instead of an amulet.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.97,0:28:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why is that sword in Zeke's possession?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.91,0:28:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And the light it's emitting...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.55,0:28:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.48,0:28:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,lt was rude of me to unsheathe a sword in front of a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.62,0:28:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.56,0:28:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,lf he has that sword, then could he be...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.66,0:29:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Could Zeke be a Baron by blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.27,0:29:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A Baron...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.91,0:29:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's just thunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.08,0:29:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you a little old to be scared of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.78,0:29:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary things are scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.95,0:29:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.39,0:29:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, him, he looked so scared outside the window all alone, so l brought him inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.49,0:29:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,lsn't he cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.13,0:29:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.05,0:30:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,l lack power... l lack the power to kill that Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.02,0:30:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll give me your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.52,0:30:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nothing to fear. You will become one with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.12,0:30:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, open your souls and lend me your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.27,0:30:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stick together, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.88,0:30:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Flare!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.89,0:31:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Come now, give me your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.16,0:31:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mineru!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.30,0:31:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.47,0:31:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,l live by the sword and serve the sword: Neris.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.87,0:31:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.99,0:31:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's the evil crusher master sword, Vigor Blade Lague.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.23,0:31:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, it appears it doesn't respect you as its wielder.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.53,0:31:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the sword is real, you cannot defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.27,0:31:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And once l suck out your life force, l'll be able to defeat Baron Zeke.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.64,0:31:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Squirm, wriggle in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.61,0:32:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do so and your life force will strengthen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.62,0:32:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And when l suck it in...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.46,0:32:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's far enough, Ternel!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.03,0:32:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster which has survived 300 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.03,0:32:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,l know not how you broke your seal,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.84,0:32:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but l, Baron Zeke, will seal you into the depths of darkness anew!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.41,0:32:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.84,0:32:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack me if you think you can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.79,0:32:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Zeke? You can't attack me now, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.23,0:32:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about us! Kill her, Zeke!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.00,0:32:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill her! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.10,0:32:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you just standing there for?! Zeke!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.84,0:33:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems you can't do it. How about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.52,0:33:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop hurting them. l admit defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.29,0:33:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This day has finally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.73,0:33:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My curse from 300 years ago shall rip open your body and offer your heart to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.20,0:33:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This world shall become the World of Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.80,0:33:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,''Him''?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.47,0:33:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't concern you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.34,0:33:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Zeke!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.75,0:33:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm gonna take my time killing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.52,0:33:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm gonna squeeze every last drop of the Baron blood out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.76,0:33:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Zeke... Zeke!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.57,0:34:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.88,0:34:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Flare!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.05,0:34:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! That sword can only be used by the chosen one!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.02,0:34:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Put it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.26,0:34:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,l don't have time to be chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.53,0:34:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,l'll be the one doing the choosing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.93,0:34:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold, sword, lend me your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.25,0:34:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.61,0:34:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This... This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.55,0:34:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,lmpossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.89,0:34:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's your chance to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.86,0:35:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,l've got something else in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.43,0:35:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? ls it morning already?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.70,0:35:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it down, lemme sleep some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.67,0:35:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! Polarine!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.78,0:35:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.91,0:35:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! What the heck happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.41,0:35:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,l dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.25,0:35:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, where's Lord Zeke? Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.65,0:35:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord Zeke!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.75,0:36:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Zeke, what's with all those girls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.49,0:36:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You really have no morals to two-time me with those girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.06,0:36:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,l know we haven't done that yet, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.99,0:36:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, ladies, lemme drive you to town.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.86,0:36:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But our hearts are connected as one, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.10,0:36:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Wait for me, Lord Zeke!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.90,0:36:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Polarine! What about the luggage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.50,0:36:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Your luggage is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.34,0:36:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no place to go. Please let us go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.81,0:36:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not? Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.72,0:36:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.02,0:36:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.65,0:36:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it have to be so cramped?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.83,0:36:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There's plenty of room back here, Polarine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.13,0:36:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm fine here, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.10,0:36:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.54,0:36:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.01,0:36:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,l must see her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.38,0:37:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The sword chose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.95,0:37:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The master of the sword is also my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.25,0:37:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,For as long as l shall live, l, Neris, will swear fealty to you.
